data.title: Andrzej Bialko, Herman Engels, Polish Radio Choir: van Nuffel: In Convertendo Dominus for Choir and Organ on Prelude
data.meta_description: Andrzej Bialko, Herman Engels, Polish Radio Choir: van Nuffel: In Convertendo Dominus for Choir and Organ featured on Prelude with Robyn Rodriquez on 11 October 2020 on Bay FM - 99.9FM
data.text:
Welcome to Prelude - a new show for Bayfm and for me. You'll hear music from several genres including film and the theatre - but mostly classical. I hope it will be a lovely start for your Sundays.

And if you'd like to contact me please do, at [email protected]. I take requests!
